      <ol>
        <li>Beneficiary name: MNNIT Alumni Association</li>

        <li>Account No. 718401011006387</li>

        <li>Account Type: Saving</li>

        <li>Branch Code 7184</li>

        <li>IFSC: VIJB0007184</li>

        <li>Swift Code: VIJBINBBRSM</li>
      </ol> 

      <p>The payment details may be sent to <a href="mailto:mnnitalumni@gmail.com">mnnitalumni@gmail.com</a> with cc to ramesh@mnnit.ac.in</p>

      <p>Cheques / DDs (hard copy) may be sent at following office address: <br>

        <span style="color: #DD5138;">MNNIT Alumni Association, Executive Development Centre (Guest House)<br>

        Residential Campus, MNNIT Allahabad – 211004</span>
      </p>  
      <div>
      <% if current_user.nil? or current_user.id_card_request.nil? %>
        <%= link_to "Register for ID Card now", idcard_register_path, class: "btn btn-info btn-login" %>
      <% elsif current_user.id_card.nil? %>
        <strong>Your request for an ID card is under process.</strong>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    </div>

  </div>
  
</div>
<% end %>

	</div>
</div>
